OL,3,CNew council leader acknowledges 'big
OL,4,Cmistake' in local brothel visit
OL,6,FThe new leader of Wales' smallest
OL,7,Flocal authority says he has learned
OL,8,Flessons from a "big mistake" he made
OL,9,Fby visiting a local brothel nine years
OL,10,Fago.
OL,12,FLabour's Councillor Brent Carter has
OL,13,Fbecome the local authority's third
OL,14,Fleader in less than three years, with
OL,15,Fcontrol of the council this week
OL,16,Freturning to Labour for the first time
OL,17,Fsince 2017.
