OL,3,CNew council leader acknowledges 'big
OL,4,Cmistake' in local brothel visit
OL,6,FOn his first day in office, Cllr
OL,7,FCarter acknowledged mistakes made in
OL,8,Fthe past, referring to an incident in
OL,9,F2015 when police found him at a local
OL,10,Fbrothel.
OL,12,FCllr Carter - then a serving
OL,13,Fcouncillor - faced no criminal charge
OL,14,Ffor the incident, and a Public
OL,15,FServices Ombudsman for Wales
OL,16,Finvestigation found that he did not
OL,17,Fbring his office or authority into
OL,18,Fdisrepute.
