OL,3,CNew council leader acknowledges 'big
OL,4,Cmistake' in local brothel visit
OL,6,F"It was a massive learning curve and a
OL,7,Fhuge mistake, an error of judgement,"
OL,8,Fhe told ITV Cymru Wales.
OL,10,F"For me, I think life is all about
OL,11,Fmaking mistakes and learning from
OL,12,Fthose mistakes and putting it right.
OL,14,F"It's given me a self-resilience and a
OL,15,Fnew perspective on how to move things
OL,16,Fforward.
OL,18,F"I want to address that now and say
OL,19,Feverybody makes errors, we can all
OL,20,Fmake mistakes, we're human beings.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
