OL,6,FCllr Carter was first elected to
OL,7,Frepresent the Plymouth ward in Merthyr
OL,8,Fin 2008, and has been re-elected three
OL,9,Ftimes, serving in the cabinet of the
OL,10,Flast Labour administration of Merthyr
OL,11,Fcouncil, which ended in 2017 when
OL,12,Fcontrol of the council switched from
OL,13,FLabour to Independent.
