OL,6,F"Since that incident in 2015, I've
OL,7,Fbeen elected another twice so I've had
OL,8,Fthe support from my residents. They
OL,9,Ftrust me, and that's what I want to
OL,10,Ftry to get across to everybody in
OL,11,FMerthyr Tydfil: you can trust me
OL,12,Fbecause I'll do my best to work for
OL,13,Feverybody in this county borough.
OL,15,F"I think everybody deserves a second
OL,16,Fchance.
