OL,6,F"We have all made mistakes across our
OL,7,Flives - some bigger than others - and
OL,8,Fmine obviously was a big mistake,
OL,9,Fsomething which I'm going to learn
OL,10,Ffrom. A second chance is what I've
OL,11,Fgot."
OL,13,FThe change in leadership this week
OL,14,Fcame after former leader Geraint
OL,15,FThomas, an Independent, stepped down
OL,16,Ffollowing a recent by-election
OL,17,Fresulting in a Labour gain from the
OL,18,FIndependents and two councillors
OL,19,Fleaving the latter group.
