OL,6,FCllr Carter said it was a "huge honour
OL,7,Fand great privilege" to become council
OL,8,Fleader, saying: "I want to do the best
OL,9,FI possibly can to serve the residents
OL,10,Fof Merthyr Tydfil.
OL,12,F"I think it's vitally important we
OL,13,Fwork together across the chamber and I
OL,14,Fdon't think we've had that for the
OL,15,Flast few years which has been
OL,16,Fdisappointing, I suppose.
OL,18,F"I am acutely aware of the budget
OL,19,Fsetting and we need to hit the ground
OL,20,Frunning really quickly with regards to
OL,21,Fthat.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
