OL,6,FThe new leader told a full council
OL,7,Fmeeting on Wednesday, 18 September:
OL,8,F"We are here to witness a change of
OL,9,Fadministration and the introduction of
OL,10,Fa change of leadership style, one that
OL,11,Fwill be resilient and dynamic which
OL,12,Fwill transform the authority into a
OL,13,Ffit-for-purpose organisation ready for
OL,14,Fthe challenges that lie ahead.
OL,16,F"As an administration, we must be
OL,17,Frealistic, honest and above all
OL,18,Ftransparent.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
