OL,6,F"We will actively listen to people's
OL,7,Fopinions by being open about the
OL,8,Fdifficult choices we may face.
OL,10,F"We see this as key to meeting the
OL,11,Ffinancial challenges that we know
OL,12,Fawait us going forward
OL,14,F"I am acutely aware the organisation
